# AI-CRM Platform — Project Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A **modular, AI-powered, multi-tenant CRM platform** from scratch.

---

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[React Frontend :5174] -->|API proxy /api| B[FastAPI Backend :8080]
    B --> C[(PostgreSQL :5432)]
    B --> D[ML Models - joblib]
    B --> E[APScheduler]
    E --> D
    E --> C
```

---

## Backend — FastAPI

### 13 API Routers (all registered under `/api/v1`)

| Router | Route prefix | Description |
|---|---|---|
| [auth.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/auth.py) | `/auth` | JWT login, register, `/me` |
| [tenants.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/tenants.py) | `/tenants` | Super admin tenant CRUD |
| [customers.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/customers.py) | `/customers` | Tenant-isolated customer CRUD |
| [leads.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/leads.py) | `/leads` | Lead CRUD + AI score field |
| [pipeline.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/models/pipeline.py) | `/pipeline` | Stages + Deals (Kanban) |
| [activities.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/activities.py) | `/activities` | Activity log + Communication logs |
| [alerts.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/alerts.py) | `/alerts` | Alerts CRUD + rule CRUD |
| [analytics.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/analytics.py) | `/analytics` | Dashboard KPIs, revenue trend, funnel |
| [ml.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/ml.py) | `/ml` | All AI/ML endpoints |
| [config.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/config.py) | `/config` | Module toggles, terminology, custom fields |
| [plugins.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/plugins.py) | `/plugins` | Plugin enable/disable per tenant |
| [tags.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/tags.py) | `/tags` | Tag CRUD + tenant user management |
| [scraper.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/routers/scraper.py) | `/scraper` | Market news + competitor price scrapers |

### 5 ML Modules

| Module | Algorithm | Output |
|---|---|---|
| [lead_scoring.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/ml/lead_scoring.py) | Random Forest | Score 0-100, priority label |
| [sales_forecast.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/ml/sales_forecast.py) | Holt-Winters (Exponential Smoothing) | 3-month revenue forecast |
| [segmentation.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/ml/segmentation.py) | KMeans (RFM features) | Segment label per customer |
| [churn_prediction.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/ml/churn_prediction.py) | Logistic Regression | Churn probability + risk level |
| [recommendation.py](file:///c:/Users/naveen/Desktop/anittaproject/backend/app/ml/recommendation.py) | Item-item Collaborative Filtering | Product recommendations |

### Alert System
- **Rule Engine** — evaluates JSON-defined rules against customer data
- **APScheduler** — runs 3 background jobs: rule alerts (hourly), inactive customers (daily), ML churn alerts (every 6h)

---

## Frontend — React + Vite

### 9 Pages

| Page | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| Login | `/login` | Auth form with demo credentials panel |
| Dashboard | `/` | KPI cards + Recharts (area, pie, bar) |
| Customers | `/customers` | Table + search + Add modal |
| Leads | `/leads` | Table + AI score A/B/C badges + batch scoring |
| Pipeline | `/pipeline` | Kanban columns per stage, deal cards |
| Activities | `/activities` | Timeline feed with type icons |
| AI Insights | `/ai-insights` | Forecast chart + RFM pie + churn risk table |
| Alerts | `/alerts` | Alert list (ack/resolve) + rule builder |
| Config | `/config` | Module toggles, terminology view, custom fields |
| Super Admin | `/admin` | Tenant card grid (super_admin only) |

### Tech Stack
- React 18 + Vite + React Router v6
- Zustand (auth state, persisted to localStorage)
- Axios with auto-auth interceptor + 401 auto-logout
- Recharts (AreaChart, BarChart, PieChart)
- Lucide React icons + react-hot-toast

